title: [Argaine's General Store]
[Argaine's Outfitting]
description: A gilt-edged steel armet hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and a modwir beam ceiling rises overhead.  A pile of unmarked crates sits in one corner of a knotty pine floor.  There is a gold-veined black marble counter on one side of the shop and a plain wooden table on the other.
